---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import Header from '../../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../../components/Footer.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Terms & Conditions — wordcountergo.com"
  description="Terms and conditions for using wordcountergo.com free online word counter tool. Understand your rights and responsibilities when using our service."
  keywords="terms and conditions, terms of service, word counter terms, free word counter, online word counter terms, wordcountergo terms"
>
  <Header />

  <main id="main-content" aria-label="Main content" class="mx-auto max-w-[900px] px-4 sm:px-6 pt-16 sm:pt-24 pb-16 sm:pb-32">
    <div class="text-center mb-16">
      <span class="inline-flex items-center px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full bg-canvas-soft text-caption text-body font-mono uppercase tracking-wider mb-4 border border-hairline">Legal</span>
      <h1 class="text-display-xl max-sm:text-[28px] max-sm:leading-[34px] sm:text-[56px] sm:leading-[56px] font-semibold tracking-[-2.4px] text-ink">Terms &amp; Conditions.</h1>
      <p class="mt-3 text-body-lg text-body max-w-lg mx-auto">Last updated: January 2025</p>
    </div>

    <div class="space-y-8 text-body-md text-body leading-relaxed">
      <section>
        <h2 class="text-display-sm font-semibold tracking-[-0.6px] text-ink mb-3">1. Acceptance of Terms</h2>
        <p>By accessing or using wordcountergo.com ("the Website"), you agree to be bound by these Terms & Conditions. If you do not agree with any part of these terms, you may not use our services.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-display-sm font-semibold tracking-[-0.6px] text-ink mb-3">2. Description of Service</h2>
        <p><a href="/" class="text-link hover:text-link-deep transition-colors">wordcountergo.com</a> provides a free online word counter and character counter tool that processes text entirely in your browser. We offer the following features:</p>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 mt-2 space-y-1">
          <li>Real-time word and character counting.</li>
          <li>Sentence, paragraph, and page counting.</li>
          <li>Readability scores (Flesch Reading Ease, Flesch-Kincaid Grade Level, Gunning Fog Index).</li>
          <li>Keyword density analysis.</li>
          <li>Social media character limit checking.</li>
          <li>Find and replace functionality.</li>
          <li>Case conversion tools.</li>
          <li>File upload support for PDF, DOCX, and TXT files.</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-display-sm font-semibold tracking-[-0.6px] text-ink mb-3">3. Privacy and Data Processing</h2>
        <p>All text processing is performed client-side in your browser. We do not store, transmit, or have access to any text you enter into the word counter. For full details, see our <a href="/privacy" class="text-link hover:text-link-deep transition-colors">Privacy Policy</a>.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-display-sm font-semibold tracking-[-0.6px] text-ink mb-3">4. User Responsibilities</h2>
        <p>You agree to use the Website only for lawful purposes and in a way that does not infringe the rights of others. You must not:</p>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 mt-2 space-y-1">
          <li>Attempt to disrupt or compromise the Website's functionality.</li>
          <li>Use automated scripts, bots, or scrapers to access the service.</li>
          <li>Upload or process content that is illegal, harmful, or infringes intellectual property rights.</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-display-sm font-semibold tracking-[-0.6px] text-ink mb-3">5. Intellectual Property</h2>
        <p>The Website, its design, logo, and content are owned by wordcountergo.com. You may not reproduce, distribute, or create derivative works without our express permission. The word counter tool itself is provided for personal and commercial use free of charge.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-display-sm font-semibold tracking-[-0.6px] text-ink mb-3">6. Disclaimer of Warranties</h2>
        <p>The service is provided "as is" and "as available" without any warranties, express or implied. While we strive for accuracy, the word count and statistics provided are estimates and should not be relied upon as absolute for legal or academic purposes. We recommend verifying important word counts with your target platform's native counter.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-display-sm font-semibold tracking-[-0.6px] text-ink mb-3">7. Limitation of Liability</h2>
        <p>wordcountergo.com shall not be liable for any indirect, incidental, special, consequential, or punitive damages arising from your use of the Website. In no event shall our total liability exceed the amount you have paid to use the service (which is zero, as the service is free).</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-display-sm font-semibold tracking-[-0.6px] text-ink mb-3">8. Changes to Terms</h2>
        <p>We reserve the right to modify these terms at any time. Changes will be effective immediately upon posting to this page. Your continued use of the Website after any changes constitutes acceptance of the new terms.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-display-sm font-semibold tracking-[-0.6px] text-ink mb-3">9. Governing Law</h2>
        <p>These terms shall be governed by and construed in accordance with the laws, without regard to its conflict of law provisions.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-display-sm font-semibold tracking-[-0.6px] text-ink mb-3">10. Contact</h2>
        <p>For questions about these terms, please <a href="/contact" class="text-link hover:text-link-deep transition-colors">contact us</a>.</p>
      </section>
    </div>
  </main>

  <Footer />
</BaseLayout>
